title: description
Lil Wayne & Static Major's Skip & Go Nak: A sweet variant of the Skip & Go Naked. As homo as Lil Wayne & Static Major's bottom.

title: notes
Lil Wayne & Static Major's Skip & Go Nak: Gin, Lemon and a dash of bottom.

title: pairing
Lil Wayne & Static Major's Skip & Go Nak: Lil Wayne & Static Major have it with a lovely Gebackene Kartoffeln and kouign-amann.

title: serving_suggestion
Lil Wayne & Static Major's Skip & Go Nak: Fill with beer, ice. Drink to the hot sounds of Lollipop.
